ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ── Optional: 0-cost dynamic translation (src/free_translate.py) ─────────────
# Leave both of these unset to use the default backend — the free, unofficial
# Google Translate web endpoint (no signup, no key, works out of the box).
#
# To switch to DeepL's official Free API tier instead (genuinely free, but
# requires a free key from https://www.deepl.com/pro-api), uncomment both:
# FINCLARIX_TRANSLATE_PROVIDER=deepl
# DEEPL_API_KEY=your-free-deepl-key-here
